<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  {% set sp = layout.spacing %}
  <style>
    @page { size: A4; margin: {{ sp.page_margin }}; }
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: {{ sp.font_size }}pt; color: #111; line-height: {{ sp.line_height }}; }
    table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; }

    .logo-name { font-size: {{ sp.font_size | int + 3 }}pt; font-weight: bold; color: #1e3a5f; border-left: 4px solid #1e3a5f; padding-left: 8px; }
    .sender-info { font-size: {{ sp.font_size | int - 1 }}pt; color: #444; padding-left: 12px; margin-top: 4px; }
    .recipient-name { font-size: {{ sp.font_size | int + 1 }}pt; font-weight: bold; color: #111; text-align: right; }
    .recipient-info { font-size: {{ sp.font_size | int - 1 }}pt; color: #444; text-align: right; }
    .city-date { font-size: {{ sp.font_size | int - 1 }}pt; color: #444; text-align: right; margin-top: 6px; }

    .logo-name-right { font-size: {{ sp.font_size | int + 3 }}pt; font-weight: bold; color: #1e3a5f; border-right: 4px solid #1e3a5f; padding-right: 8px; text-align: right; }
    .sender-info-right { font-size: {{ sp.font_size | int - 1 }}pt; color: #444; padding-right: 12px; margin-top: 4px; text-align: right; }
    .recipient-name-left { font-size: {{ sp.font_size | int + 1 }}pt; font-weight: bold; color: #111; }
    .recipient-info-left { font-size: {{ sp.font_size | int - 1 }}pt; color: #444; }
    .city-date-left { font-size: {{ sp.font_size | int - 1 }}pt; color: #444; margin-top: 6px; }

    .objet { font-size: {{ sp.font_size }}pt; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .objet strong { color: #1e3a5f; }
    hr { border: none; border-top: 2px solid #1e3a5f; margin: 10px 0 14px 0; }
    h1 { font-size: {{ sp.font_size | int + 2 }}pt; text-align: center; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; color: #1e3a5f; margin: 0 0 4px 0; }
    .subtitle { text-align: center; font-size: {{ sp.font_size | int - 1 }}pt; color: #555; margin-bottom: 14px; }
    .sec { font-size: {{ sp.font_size | int - 1 }}pt; font-weight: bold; color: #1e3a5f; border-left: 3px solid #1e3a5f; padding-left: 6px; margin: {{ sp.section_mb }}px 0 5px 0; }
    .amt td { padding: {{ sp.cell_padding_v }}px {{ sp.cell_padding_h }}px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; font-size: {{ sp.font_size }}pt; }
    .amt td.r { text-align: right; }
    .amt tr.tot td { font-weight: bold; background: #eef2f7; border-top: 2px solid #1e3a5f; }
    .closing { font-size: {{ sp.font_size | int - 1 }}pt; color: #555; margin-top: 16px; text-align: center; }
    .legal { font-size: 7.5pt; color: #aaa; margin-top: 14px; border-top: 1px solid #e5e5e5; padding-top: 6px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <table style="margin-bottom: {{ sp.header_mb }}px;">
    <tr>
      <td style="width: 52%; vertical-align: top; padding-right: 16px;">
        {% for block in layout.header_left %}
          {% if block == 'logo' %}
          <div class="logo-name">Le Comptoir Immo</div>
          {% elif block == 'sender' %}
          <div class="sender-info">
            {% if property %}{{ property.owner_name }}<br>{{ property.full_address }}{% else %}Gestion locative{% endif %}
          </div>
          {% elif block == 'recipient' %}
          <div class="recipient-name-left">{{ tenant_names if tenant_names else (avis.tenant.full_name if avis.tenant else '') }}</div>
          <div class="recipient-info-left">
            {% if property %}{{ property.name }}<br>{{ property.full_address }}{% endif %}
          </div>
          {% elif block == 'citydate' %}
          <div class="city-date-left">{% if property and property.city %}{{ property.city }}, {% endif %}le {{ today }}</div>
          {% endif %}
        {% endfor %}
      </td>
      <td style="width: 48%; vertical-align: top; padding-left: 16px;">
        {% for block in layout.header_right %}
          {% if block == 'logo' %}
          <div class="logo-name-right">Le Comptoir Immo</div>
          {% elif block == 'sender' %}
          <div class="sender-info-right">
            {% if property %}{{ property.owner_name }}<br>{{ property.full_address }}{% else %}Gestion locative{% endif %}
          </div>
          {% elif block == 'recipient' %}
          <div class="recipient-name">{{ tenant_names if tenant_names else (avis.tenant.full_name if avis.tenant else '') }}</div>
          <div class="recipient-info">
            {% if property %}{{ property.name }}<br>{{ property.full_address }}{% endif %}
          </div>
          {% elif block == 'citydate' %}
          <div class="city-date">{% if property and property.city %}{{ property.city }}, {% endif %}le {{ today }}</div>
          {% endif %}
        {% endfor %}
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  <div class="objet">
    <strong>Objet :</strong> Avis d'échéance — {{ avis.period_label if avis.period_label else '' }}
  </div>

  <hr>

  <h1>Avis d'échéance</h1>
  <p class="subtitle">{{ avis.period_label if avis.period_label else '' }}</p>

  <div class="sec">Détail du loyer</div>
  <table class="amt">
    <tr><td>Loyer hors charges</td><td class="r">{{ "%.2f" | format(avis.amount_rent | float) }} €</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Charges récupérables</td><td class="r">{{ "%.2f" | format(avis.amount_charges | float) }} €</td></tr>
    {% if avis.amount_apl and avis.amount_apl | float > 0 %}
    <tr><td>Déduction APL (tiers-payant CAF)</td><td class="r">- {{ "%.2f" | format(avis.amount_apl | float) }} €</td></tr>
    {% endif %}
    <tr class="tot"><td>Total à régler</td><td class="r">{{ "%.2f" | format(avis.amount_due | float) }} €</td></tr>
  </table>

  {% if avis.due_date %}
  <div class="sec">Date limite de paiement</div>
  <table class="amt">
    <tr><td>À régler avant le</td><td class="r">{{ avis.due_date.strftime('%d/%m/%Y') }}</td></tr>
  </table>
  {% endif %}

  <p class="closing">
    Nous vous remercions de bien vouloir procéder au règlement de cette somme dans les délais impartis.<br>
    Pour toute question, n'hésitez pas à nous contacter.
  </p>

  <div class="legal">
    Document généré par Le Comptoir Immo — Gestion locative.
    Cet avis d'échéance est établi conformément aux dispositions du bail en vigueur.
  </div>

</body>
</html>
